1.title: Mille Crepes
1.description: Seasonal fruits generously packed between six layers of crepe. Our most popular item.

2.title: Strawberry Cake
2.description: Big juicy strawberries in fresh whipped cream snuggled between layers of sponge cake. The ultimate experience.

3.title: Fresh Fruits Cake
3.description: An extravaganza of fresh fruit and cream puff pastry, set between layers of sponge cake.

4.title: Blueberry Cheese Tart
4.description: A whipped cream cheese mousse lathered with fresh berries.

5.title: Green Tea Mousse
5.description: A bittersweet organic green tea mousse with sweet azuki beans, enveloped in fresh whipped cream.

6.title: Sakura Cake
6.description: Sweet azuki beans enveloped in a delicate sakura cherry blossom flavored mousse, decorated with sugared cherry blossoms.

7.title: Melon Cake
7.description: Sponge cake smothered with slices of ripe melon and fresh whipped cream, covered with a layer of whole cream.

8.title: Strawberry Chocolate Cake
8.description: Layers of bitter chocolate sponge cake packed with juicy strawberries in our special whipped cream.

9.title: Marron Tart
9.description: Chocolate chips in fresh whipped cream fill the base of the tart, topped with generous lumps of chestnut cream.

11.title: Chocolate Cake
11.description: Chocolate sponge cake smothered in chocolate cream and walnuts, with a hint of brandy for that special richness.

12.title: Royal Milk Tea Cake
12.description: This dark tea sponge cake paired with cream will fill your senses with the flavor and fragrance of royal milk tea.

13.title: Black and White Chocolate Cake
13.description: A chocolate chiffon cake baked with the fragrant presence of cashews, embellished with a rich white chocolate cream.

14.title: Mocha Cake
14.description: Bits of coffee jelly in mocha cream fill the spaces between layers of spicy cinnamon sponge cake. Ideal for the not-so-sweet tooth.

15.title: Marron Chocolate Cake
15.description: Chocolate sponge cake with just a bit of bitterness filled with sliced chestnuts in chocolate cream - lots of it.

16.title: Citron Cake
16.description: Lemon rind is baked into the sponge cake to make this zesty sandwich of fresh squeezed lemon jelly and lemon flavored mixed cream.
